casebody.data:
No. 11-7787. Victor Vevea, Petitioner v. United States. 565 U.S. 1155, 132 S. Ct. 1135,

181 L. Ed. 2d 975,

2012 U.S. LEXIS 855. January 17, 2012.

Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied. Petitioner is allowed until February 7, 2012, within which to pay the docketing fee required by Rule 38(a) and to submit a petition in compliance with Rule 33.1 of the Rules of this Court.

Same case below, 446 Fed. Appx. 63.
